3.7 Table Constructors table结构
  创建并初始化table:
  days = {"Sunday", "Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday",
          "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday"}
  days[1] = "Sunday" 因为lua的table下标是从1开始的
  
  也可以写成：
  
  a = {x=10, y=20}   <-->  a = {}; a.x=10; a.y=20
  
  原始的写法是最好的，因为lua创建table要确定table的长度
  
  不管我们怎么创建table，我们通过以下的方法添加和删除 字段：
  w = {x=0, y=0, label="console"}
  x = {math.sin(0), math.sin(1), math.sin(2)}
  w[1] = "another field" -- add key 1 to table 'w'
  x.f = w -- add key "f" to table 'x'
  print(w["x"]) --> 0
  print(w[1]) --> another field
  print(x.f[1]) --> another field  从左到右看，x.f = w, w[1]= "another field"
  w.x = nil -- remove field "x"
  
  可以在一个table里混合不同的写法：
  polyline = {color="blue",
              thickness=2,
              npoints=4,
              {x=0, y=0}, -- polyline[1]
              {x=-10, y=0}, -- polyline[2]
              {x=-10, y=1}, -- polyline[3]
              {x=0, y=1} -- polyline[4]
              }
  print(polyline[2].x) --> -10
  print(polyline[4].y) --> 1
  注意table的第三个字段开始，key是从1开始的
  
  opnames = {["+"] = "add", ["-"] = "sub",
             ["*"] = "mul", ["/"] = "div"}
  i = 20; s = "-"
  a = {[i+0] = s, [i+1] = s..s, [i+2] = s..s..s}
  print(opnames[s]) --> sub
  print(a[22]) --> ---
  
  {x=0,y=0} 相当于 {["x"]=0,["y"]=0}
  
  你可以在table的最后一个字段加逗号，例子：
    a = {[1]="red", [2]="green", [3]="blue",}
    
  你可以用分号区分两种格式，例子：
    {x=10, y=45; "one", "two", "three"}
  
  
